login

public void login(String username,
                  String password,
                  DDF_SocksProxy proxySettings)
Starts the data feed asynchronously. Notification of login success is reported by FeedStateListeners which are bound to this object.

Constructs a new feed client with the user's user name and password and a Socks5 proxy. The transport protocol defaults to TCP and a default executor are used.
